	<p>In my experience, the curse line spells have been above poison on the aggro scale. I may be wrong though. For reference, I use Bane and Blood of Saryrn as my poison and curse dots. I can't say where Uthor lies, since I haven't used it for anything but soloing.<br />
<br />
On another note, our epic dot seems to not draw any aggro that I can see. It's also more likely to stick on mobs than Bane is.</p>
	
	
	
