	<!-- message -->
	<p>If you can, exp a bit at the castle in PoFire and do this little experiment.<br />
<br />
Drop Malos and slow then :<br />
<br />
For some pulls, just use your cold DD only.<br />
For some pulls, just use your poison DD only.<br />
For some pulls, just use your disease DoTs only (try to drop 3 or 4 if you can <img src="images/smilies/wink.gif" border="0" alt="" title="wink" smilieid="5" />).<br />
For some pulls, just use your magic DoTs only (try to drop 3 or 4 too).<br />
For some pulls, just use your poison Dots only (try to drop 3 or 4 too).<br />
<br />
For the DD, with approx the same number of nukes, I was able to steal aggro. But what's funny it that with less poison nukes and so, less damage, I got aggro without trouble while I still had to cast one or two more times with the cold DD.<br />
<br />
For the Dots, even with 4 disease dots, I barely never got aggro.<br />
With the curses, got the aggro at the 3rd dot usually.<br />
And with the poison ones ? Usually, the first one was enough to get the aggro.<br />
<br />
As many said, how is it possible to steal aggro on a very well equipped warrior/pal/sk when you drop 3 dots while wizards nukes for 10k minimum in the same time and keep unnoticed by the mobs ???<br />
<br />
That always bugged me.</p>
	
	
	
		<div>__________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=48248 "> Fenril Lonewolf</a><br />
Member of Novae<br />
Prophet of The Tribunal <br />
